   - System overview and core principles
   - Architecture design patterns
   - User workflow and getting started guide
   - Directory structure
   - Troubleshooting

4. **Phase 2 docs remain available for**:
   - Historical reference
   - Understanding system evolution
   - Detailed Phase 2 implementation notes

